Sinew/Otyebis Staff:





Sinew powered down his engines, not his weapons though, and landed next to 
the small garrison of IGL soldiers.  "Follow us.  If you try anything you and 
your comrades will die."

------

Two cells opened, in one are the Stunticons and in the other is Cliffjumper.

"Follow us." said one of about twenty guards to the six robots as he headed 
out a door.
